      "message": "I\u0027m not sure what the comment is for. Are you suggesting to remove \"/type\" from the URL?\n\nGET /v2.0/notification-methods returns a list of all the currently defines notification methods. Adding query parameters to this query, should just filter the notification methods, not change the document that is returned. Just returning a list of the supported notification method types, is a new document, therefore, that is the reason for introducing a new endpoint.",
